com.google.common.io

接口 LineProcessor<T>


  • @Beta
 @GwtIncompatible
public interface LineProcessor<T>
    A callback to be used with the streaming readLines methods.

    processLine(java.lang.String) will be called for each line that is read, and should return false when you want to stop processing.

    从以下版本开始:
    1.0

      限定符和类型 方法和说明

      • processLine

        boolean processLine(String line)
             throws IOException
        This method will be called once for each line.
        参数:
        line - the line read from the input, without delimiter
        返回:
        true to continue processing, false to stop
        抛出:
        IOException
